nodes.text: The Outer Moddell systems were a group a star systems in the trailing Moddell sector of the Outer Rim Territories.
The Outer Moddell systems included Ast Kikorie, Endor, Murk, Sanyassa IV, Trindello, Kuna's Eye, Kuna's Fist, Kuna's Horn, Kuna's Tail, UR-1060, UR-2650, UR-3741, UR-8827, UR-9353, and Zorbia.
Most of the Moddell sector's traffic was found on the Annaj-Houche Run, making up the Inner Moddell systems. Traffic dropped off considerably in the Outer Moddell beyond those systems.
